                               JsonPrimaryKey parentKey,

        Create a composite JSON primary key DTO with a specified DTO class name, a parent key, and a child key.
        Parameters:
        className - the fully qualified name of the DTO class for the objects that the primary key identifies
        parentKey - a JSON primary key serving as the parent portion of the composite key
        childKey - a JSON primary key serving as the child portion of the composite key
